lead_paragraph: World number one Jordan Spieth admitted he was guilty of rushing and not playing smart as he left himself a five-shot deficit to overhaul on the final day of the Singapore Open on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Frustrated Spieth Seeks Sunday Spark to Lift Singapore Bid
